#DIM DYNAMIC 分野
#DIM DYNAMIC 技量, 4
#DIM DYNAMIC 難度, 4
#DIM DYNAMIC 難度合計
#DIM DYNAMIC 人数, 4
#DIM DYNAMIC LMEMORY
#DIM DYNAMIC LCOUNT
#DIM DYNAMIC LCOUNT2
#DIM DYNAMIC 収入, 4
